GLOSS|dogfooding|2A|Fox|Dogfooding|You really like clicking links huh? >.>\n\nNice, now I can remind you that the wiki exists! Use it, it's very fun!
GLOSS|john_adventure|1B1A1D|Fox|john_adventure|John Adventure was a guy who, contrary to his name, lived a regular life and generally got up to nothing special, ever. He works a desk job, has a turtle named Dog, and watches Friends.
GLOSS|john_adventure|1B1A1E|Fox|john_adventure|John Adventure was a guy who, contrary to his name, lived a regular life and generally got up to nothing special, ever. He works a desk job, has a turtle named Dog, and watches Friends.\n\nHe was transported to another world with a classic case of truck-related isekai and now lives as a barkeep, serving drinks to attractive anthropomorphic lizards and trying to find his way home in his spare time to get back to his turtle as soon as possible.
